                <summary>On April 2nd, General Stoneman was relieved from command in Virginia and
                    replaced with Gen. Webb. Webb immediately reinstated Wells as Governor of
                    Virginia. The paper asserts that there is no doubt the Republican Congress sent
                    Webb to Virginia specifically to reinstate the "objectionable" Wells.</summary>
                <note/>
